original_title: Kel Videos Live: This Face Belongs on the Tube
overview: Those who know Cable Ace Award winner Kel Mitchell only for Nickelodeon's "Kenan and Kel" will discover a new side to the comic in these hilarious sketches. Mitchell assumes a series of musical personalities, each more outrageous than the one before. Although each is entirely "fictional," the similarities to Prince, James Brown and others are dead-on, down to Mitchell's performance of original music.
title: Kel Videos Live: This Face Belongs on the Tube
